===[[Pokémon Mezastar]]===
Alain appeared in [[Pokémon Mezastar]].<ref>https://twitter.com/Pokemon_Meza/status/1568071704244457472</ref> In this game, Alain is seen using {{p|Chesnaught}}, {{p|Charizard}}, {{p|Weavile}}, and {{p|Tyranitar}}. In the [[Double Chain set 1 (Mezastar)|first set in the Double Chain series]], Alain also appeared as an opponent in an event that recreated the [[Masters Eight Tournament]] that ran from October 27 to November 21, 2022. Upon beating the character, the player can receive a Support Pokémon Ticket based on [[Alain's Charizard]], which can [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolve]] into Mega Charizard X.<ref>https://pokemonmezastar.com/event/e2210142/</ref>

